data.description: Charming 2 story, 4 bedroom and 2.5 bath home. Nestled in a nice community with a community park and greenbelt. Great floor plan with living room, formal dining area, family room, and large eat-in-kitchen. Abundance of ceramic tiles in entry, kitchen, family room, baths, and laundry. Upgraded laminated wood flooring on the second floor. Inviting backyard with covered patio and pavers.
